info.name: Roblox Avatar Style - Christmas Edition
info.description: Oooooh I see! Christmas and New Year's Eve costumes have arrived! Sure, what's the harm? Why should we miss out on the most beautiful time of the year, when the entire world is decked out in lights, gingerbreads, and Christmas trees? Dress up and show off your red and white costumes from your Christmas and winter wardrobe!
